snippet.title: Rockman Tennis Gameplay
snippet.description:
This is gameplay of the Wily Cup, the advanced class tournament. The EX Cup unlocks after all three cups are beaten (I still have yet to beat the intermediate Cossack Cup).
More info here: https://www.rockman-corner.com/2023/12/japan-exclusive-rockman-cellphone-games.html
